org.apache.ambari.server.actionmanager

Class HostRoleCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ambari.server.actionmanager.HostRoleCommand

  • public class HostRoleCommand
extends Object
    This class encapsulates the information for an task on a host for a particular role which action manager needs. It doesn't capture actual command and parameters, but just the stuff enough for action manager to track the request.

    Since this class is cached by the ActionDBAccessor, it should not hold references to JPA entities. It's possible that by holding onto JPA entities, they will inadvertently hold onto the entire cache of entities in the L1 cache.
